title: File:Vesteys Beach (renamed Bundilla Beach in 2021) in May 2003.jpg
author: kenhodge13
description: Vesteys Beach Darwin (renamed "Bundilla Beach", 2021) is around Bullockys Point from Mindil Beach.  A very rocky beach it is not popular for swimming and has the Darwin Water Ski Club boat ramp in the middle distance.  At the Fanny Bay end are the Darwin Yacht Club and Darwin Trailer Boat Club.
